==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Napping
<hw>Nap"ping</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
or process of raising a nap, as on cloth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Hat Making)</fld> <def>A sheet of partially felted
fur before it is united to the hat body.</def>
<rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>The act or process of having a short sleep; <as>as,
<ex>napping</ex> is a common occupation for cats</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nappy</ent>⟦br⟧
